U.S. dollars) and took away 100,000 shillings from the bar owner
and 30,000 shillings from one of the mayor's colleagues.
</P>
<P>
The vice-president ordered Arusha Regional Police Commander,
Juma Ng' wanang'wake to terminate the service of any policeman who
are found collaborating with criminals.
</P>
<P>
Arusha is an important tourist region vital for the economy of
the eastern African country and a lot of international meetings
are held there.
</P>
<P>
The factors require high state of security, he added, urging
the police to launch a special operation against crimes and common
people to cooperate.
</P>
<P>
The vice-president opened a conference of the Southern African
Development Community (SADC) early Tuesday and is expected to open
a general meeting for Council of Minister of the 14-member
organization Friday. 
