<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, June 24 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 5,096.20 on Thursday, down 39.52, or
0.77 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
