transportation bottleneck to make this mountainous province more
accessible to Chinese and overseas tourists.
</P>
<P>
Guizhou is known for its scenic forests, Karst caves, and lakes
and ethnic minority villages, but poor traffic conditions have
hindered the development of tourism in and around them.
</P>
<P>
