<TEXT>
<P>
SHENZHEN, June 24 (Xinhua) -- The coastal cities of Shenzhen in
Guangdong Province and Xiamen in Fujian Province have been moving
to protect their coastal environment.
</P>
<P>
A legislative affairs bureau official in Shenzhen says that
they drew up a 60-article regulation on marine pollution control
that will go into effect after members of the Shenzhen City People
's Congress Standing Committee pass it.
</P>
<P>
